author: Rory Jones
title: New Dispute Over Jerusalem Religious Shrine
text:
Israeli police blocked the installation of surveillance cameras inside a sensitive mosque in Jerusalem on Monday, fanning new tensions amid diplomatic efforts to stop the monthlong escalation of violence between Palestinians and Israelis.
